            <p class="text-justify">The major issues that continue to affect housing in Nigeria include legislation, high cost of land registration and titling, policy issues, licensing issues, inadequate access to finance, risk sharing mechanism among others. Save yourself the tedium and let HouseIT ease the process of you becoming a home owner</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 col-sm-12 d-flex justify-content-end">
            <img src="~/utils/svg/home-svg.svg" />
        </div>
    </div>
