                <img src="~/utils/svg/payment.svg" />
            </div>
            <h5 class="text-capitalize mb-3">payment plan</h5>
            <p class="text-justify hero-ben-txt">HouseIT offers flexible payment plan (Monthly, Quarterly and yearly) to help you achieve your life-long goal of being a home owner  </p>
